description:
This is a 22 minute workout called '20 min TOTAL BODY STRETCH ROUTINE | Muscle Recovery, Flexibility and Relaxation' from the channel fitbymik.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Join me for a 20 minute TOTAL BODY STRETCH ROUTINE for muscle recovery and relaxation. Do this sequence after your workout or on your rest day. We'll perform mostly static stretches with a few flowing movements throughout. You'll recognize a couple of familiar YOGA postures within the routine as well.
